---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Digital Advertising Sydney &#8212; Google Ads &amp; Meta Ads"
  description="SNAV Marketing runs Google Ads and Meta Ads campaigns for Sydney businesses. Targeted paid advertising that puts you in front of local customers actively searching for your services."
  canonical="/services/digital-advertising"
>
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container-lg">
      <a href="/services" class="breadcrumb">&#8592; All Services</a>
      <div class="service-icon-lg">&#127919;</div>
      <h1 class="service-title">Digital Advertising</h1>
      <p class="service-subtitle">Google Ads and Meta Ads campaigns that put your business in front of Sydney customers exactly when they're ready to buy &#8212; every dollar tracked and accountable.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Ads Audit</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-lg service-layout">
      <div class="service-main">
        <h2 class="service-h2">Stop Paying for Ads That Don't Convert</h2>
        <p class="service-body">Most Sydney businesses running Google Ads or Meta Ads are wasting money &#8212; broad targeting, no conversion tracking, ads that speak to everyone and no one. SNAV builds paid advertising campaigns with one purpose: qualified leads and sales, at a cost that makes sense for your business.</p>
        <p class="service-body">We combine smart audience targeting, compelling creative, conversion-optimised landing pages and relentless A/B testing to drive real results. Every campaign is transparent &#8212; you see exactly where your budget goes and what it returns.</p>

        <h3 class="service-h3">Google Ads</h3>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Search Ads &#8212; appear when customers search for your services in Sydney</li>
          <li>Local Service Ads &#8212; Google Guaranteed listings for tradies and services</li>
          <li>Performance Max &#8212; AI-optimised campaigns across all Google channels</li>
          <li>Display &amp; Remarketing &#8212; stay visible to website visitors across the web</li>
          <li>YouTube Ads &#8212; video advertising for awareness and brand building</li>
          <li>Google Shopping &#8212; product-based campaigns for e-commerce</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="service-h3">Meta Ads (Facebook &amp; Instagram)</h3>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Lead Generation Ads &#8212; capture enquiries without leaving the platform</li>
          <li>Traffic and Conversion Campaigns &#8212; drive bookings, calls and form fills</li>
          <li>Retargeting &#8212; re-engage website visitors and social audiences</li>
          <li>Lookalike Audiences &#8212; find new customers who mirror your best existing ones</li>
          <li>Instagram Ads &#8212; visual campaigns for product and brand visibility</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="service-h3">What Every Campaign Includes</h3>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Full account setup and conversion tracking configuration</li>
          <li>Keyword research and competitive analysis</li>
          <li>Ad copywriting and creative production</li>
          <li>Landing page recommendations (or creation)</li>
          <li>Ongoing weekly optimisations and bid management</li>
          <li>Monthly performance report with clear ROI metrics</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3 class="sidebar-heading">Get a Free Ads Audit</h3>
          <p class="sidebar-sub">Already running ads? We'll review your account for free and show you exactly where the budget is leaking &#8212; no obligation.</p>
          <ContactForm />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .service-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F 0%, #2a4f80 100%); padding: calc(4rem + 80px) 0 4.5rem; text-align: center; }
  .breadcrumb { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #7a9bbf; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .breadcrumb:hover { color: #FF6B35; }
  .service-icon-lg { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-title { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-subtitle { font-size: 1.0625rem; color: #94afc7; max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  .service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .service-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px; } }
  .service-h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-h3 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-heading); margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .service-body { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-body); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-body); }
  .service-list li::before { content: '&#10003; '; color: #FF6B35; font-weight: 700; }
  .sidebar-card { background: var(--bg-alt); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.75rem; border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); position: sticky; top: calc(80px + 1rem); }
  .sidebar-heading { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .sidebar-sub { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.6; }
</style>